headline: Is Danaher Corporation (DHR) a Quality Compounder With Long-Term Revenue Growth?
summary: Baron Funds released its “Baron Durable Advantage Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund primarily focuses on investing in securities of large-sized companies.
